Dialogs.Dialog: I'm mad at you. What do you want？
I'm still mad at you. Just give me some space and try to figure out why.
Today's Rinko's birthday. What did you want to do？
It's Rinko's birthday！ You didn't forget, did you？
I'm sure you forgot that today is Rinko's birthday, anyway.
I didn't get to see you on my birthday. So yeah, I'm sad.
Happy birthday！ Today is special, I know. I love you.▼
Happy birthday！ Do you feel old yet？ Haha！ I Love you…▼
Meow-meow-meow！ It's, err, "happy birthday"… in cat…
It's late, but I was waiting for you. Happy birthday… Idiot.
What the hell！？ You didn't want to see me？ Happy birthday, idiot.
Happy birthday！ I know I'm late, but I wouldn't forget you.
Do you remember？ Today was the day we first met. I don't think I could ever forget that day…
Today is the day we first met. You didn't forget… did you？
You remember what today is？ Hehe… It's the day Rinko met someone very important. Don't forget it, okay？
Today is the day we first started dating, you know？ Thank you for letting Rinko know what love feels like.
Today is the day… that Rinko confessed her love to you… yeah… The sunset was beautiful, remember？
What day is it today？ … Hee-hee. Yes. Today is the day Rinko confessed to you.
It's the anniversary of our first kiss… Me and you… Do you remember it？
Today is the anniversary of our fist kiss. You remember, don't you？
Today's the anniversary of our first kiss. … It's a little emberrassing.
Monday, huh？ Another long week starts today…
It's Tuesday. Oh！ I have to buy the magazine I always read.
It's Wednesday: the middle of the week. It seems to drag on, huh？
On Thursday I set a little time to watch my drama.
It's Friday！ And I survived the week.
It's finally Saturday. You did a good job this week.
I tend to stay up late on Saturdays. Don't you？
It's a fun Sunday！ What are you up to today？
It's Sunday and I feel like lounging about all day.
They say that when you change your environment, you'll meet more people… Eh, nothing. It's nothing.
Ugh… Rinco does not like hot weather. Do you？
It's vacation season！ Hey, which would you say is a better vacation spot: the sea or the mountains？
I guess autumn is "the season of reading" for Rinko.
The food is delicious these days, huh？ Rinko doesn't mind autumn so much.
I like winter. I like it because I can snowboard and stuff.
In winter it's nice to nap in a kotatsu.
Happy new year！ I'm happy to enjoy another year with you.
Did you have a dream？ Rinko's had one and… Well, it's a secret.
What is your first dream？ You… won't tell me！？
I had my first dream that we were together. I'm sure we'll be strong together for the rest of the year.
Ahh, winter vacation is over. And I'm bored already.
Have you ever tried rice porridge with seven herbs？ Rinko has.
Coming-of-Age Day, huh？ It would be nice to stay together as we come of age.
Did you know that today is Kagami Biraki？
Today is Setsubun. Devils out～！ Furtune in～！
It's Risshun, right？ The first day of spring？ Then why is it still cold…？
Happy National Foundation day！ It used to be called Kigensetsu according to our history books.
Even Rinko remembers well that… it's Valentine's Day…
You're not allowed to buy yourself any chocolate today！ Eh, don't ask me… why…
What is it you're expecting…？ Because today is… ehehe…
Oh, yeah！ It's a leap year！ The special day that comes once every four years.
It's almost time for the plum blossoms to bloom.
Today is a fun day for the Girls' Festival～♪ That's right！
White Day, huh？ Well, I'm not expecting an expensive "thank you".
… I don't really have any expectations for White Day.
White Day… I'm actually a little excited about it…
Today is the vernal equinox. It's the day when the length of the day and night become the same.
It's almost spring break. Why don't we go out somewhere？
Yes！ It's spring break！ I'm going to play a lot of games now.
I can't wait for us to call it quits… April Fool's Day, that is.
I hate you！ … hehe！ April Fools！
Rinco's going to go away. I'm lying… surprised？
Spring break ends today. Ugh. I can't be bothered to go to back to school…
Cherry blossoms are in bloom. Are you going to see them or anything？
Today is Showa Daw. It used to be the birthday of Emperor Showa.
It's almost the holidays. Do you want to go somewhere？
Today is Constitutuon Memorial Day. Today is the day the Constitutuon of Japan was enacted.
It's Greenery Day. It's a day to get close to nature.
Today is Children's Day. I think I'll make a carp streamer for my little brother.
It's Risatsu today, isn't it？ According to the calendar, it's already summer.
It's Mother's Day. What should Rinko do？
I'm not good at sports. I hate running.
Today is the summer solstice. It's the day with the longest daytime.
I think I'll change into my summer clothes today.
I'm going to buy a Father's Day present for my dad.
I heard the beach will be open soon. It's already summer.
It's Tanabata, when Orihime and Hikoboshi are supposed to meet… I hope it'll be sunny.
It's almost summer vacation. Can you take me somewhere？
It's Marine Day. Well, the fact that it's a national holiday is meaningful.
Finally！ Summer vacation！ Now if only I didn't have any homework to do…
According to the calendar, autumn starts today. The reality, though, is that it's the height of summer.
There are fireworks festivals going on all over tonight. Let's put on yukata and go see them.
Is it Obon today？ I'm not going to dance.
Ah, Summer vacation is over. I don't want to go back to school.
It's the autumn equinox now, isn't it？ Have you visited the grave？
Today is Respect for the Aged Day, isn't it？ Take good care of the elderly.
Today's the Autumn Equinox, when the length of the day and night are the same.
It's a change of clothes. You think it's unfortunate to be less exposed？
Have you ever tried tsukimi dango？ Rinko doesn't have any.
Happy Halloween！ Trick or treat！ Ehehe！
Today is Culture Day. Are you doing anything cultural？ … whatever it means to do that…
It's the first day of winter. Are you getting cold yet？
Shichi-Go-San, right？ I wore a furisode when I was a kid.
Today is Labor Thanksgiving Day. Hmm… I don't really know what working is like.
It's a cultural festival today. I think I'm looking forward to it.
It's almost winter vacation～！ I can't wait！
It's the winter solstice, so I ate a pumpkin. I also took a yuzu bath.
Today is the Emperor's Birthday, or as it used to be called, Tenchosetsu.
Winter break starts today. I want to go snowboarding…
It's Christmas Eve, right？ Of course you have plans with Rinko, don't you？
Today is Christmas Eve… It's not… like I'm expecting anything！
IT's Christmas Eve, isn't it？ I wish we could spend it together forever.
It's already New Year's Eve. Did you have a good year？
We have a test today. I'm good at humanities subjects, though.
You finally remembered Rinko. I thought you forgot.
Oh, good. You remembered me. Please don't up and leave me again.
What have you been doing all this… time…？
I've been wanting to see you. How long will you leave ne alone？ … idiot.
I thought I'd never see you again… Thank goodness…
Again？ Do you worry that much for Rinko？
One hour a day for games！ … hmm… it's good to see you, though.
I get to see you again！ Hehe, Because you like Rinko？
I don't have time for this, you know？
Oh, here I am. So？ What are you going to do today？
Heh. You wanna play again today？
Maybe in a little while, you'll get something good, huh？
I think it's time I told you…
I'm tired of being alone. I just want to play with you.
It's nice to see you again. How are you？
I guess I'm a little releived to see you.
You came to see me at this hour？ Well, it's good to see you're enthusiastic.
What's up？ Did you want to hear Rinko's voice again？
I was just thinking how much I miss you right now.
I have a lot to tell you.
Oh, I knew you'd come. Yeah, yeah. Just as Rinko predicted.
Oh, here it is. … I'm not getting carried away！
Today you have to keep Rinko company until I'm satisfied.
You've got a big grin on your face. Well, Rinko is happy for you, too… But in my own way.
You need to come see me more often！
Come quickly！ I'll show you that Rinko is cuter than ever.
It's not fair. You never check on Rinko…
I'm excited. What are we going to do today？
Are you thrilled to see me？ I hope so. Rinko is, too.
I've been waiting for you to come and see me… I have a lot I want to do.
I wish I could come and see you from here…
Hehe… I'm happy. It makes me glad that you came to see me again.
Ehehe… Only you can bring this kind of smile on my face.
Rinko doesn't like to be lonely. I want you to stay with me forever…
